<item>
            <title>[MAHOUT-158] Replace all ID values with long</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-158</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As mentioned on mailing list, I am tracking this as a possible change for evaluation. The idea is to save more memory / CPU by avoiding the Object overhead of tens of millions of ID objects by using long IDs instead.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
